                           In Amharic; written in 1930 E.C. (= 1937/38 A.D.).
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#121va">Fol. 121va</locus>: Inventory of paraphernalia donated by ʾabeto Wäldä Śǝllase (?).<q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           In Gǝʿǝz and Amharic; in the same hand as that of Additio 4.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#121vb">Fol. 121vb</locus>: Inventory of the church properties.<q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
